title: 'DO NOT GET FOOLED WITH LOW PRICE'
body: All the tapes that are delivered are on the verge of getting finished. There's hardly anything on them. You can compare the thickness of tapes shown on the product page, to the video of tapes posted in the review section, you could clearly see the difference. Don't get fooled with low price..delivered tapes aren't even worth that much.
